{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dbebc62431","title":"工农群众学习马克思主义理论的高潮","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"040cf722df","index":0,"year":1958,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"dbebc62431"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","name":"红旗一九五八年第六期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"ba0474c16b","name":"《红旗》杂志编辑部"}]},"publication_details":{"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9a9a00c2f4","type":"paragraph","text":"理始一旦掌握了群众，便立刻成为物贸的力量","index":0,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"e77a43ccbc","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思工农群众学习属克思主义理输的高潮","index":1,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"6dd23f1f81","type":"paragraph","text":"随着经济建设的高潮的到来，不可避免地将要出现一个文化建设的高潮。中国人被人韶为不文明的时代已经过去了，我们将以一个具有高度文化的民族出现于世界。","index":2,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"02bf75b1f1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"f50c41e3c0","type":"paragraph","text":"工人农民学习理输的租藏如雨后套争","index":4,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"159bc77d48","type":"paragraph","text":"在社会主义建设大跃进的形势下，广大工农群众据起了一个学居克思主义理、学毛泽东同志膏作的高潮。","index":5,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"f22d9aa34b","type":"paragraph","text":"近两个月来，各地工人群众学哲学的粗锻迅速地发层起素。这里常一些例子","index":6,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"95851e155f","type":"paragraph","text":"上海求新造船厂三个月前建立了第一个哲学自学小粗，有十五个工人参加，现在已越发展到三十四个，四百多人。","index":7,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"1aa73a78d5","type":"paragraph","text":"哈尔滨市在一个月内就粗成了三千多个哲学学习小粗，有七施","index":8,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"9496611b63","type":"paragraph","text":"万多工人参加学习，并且还开办了一个工人业余哲学学习班，学东","index":9,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"2fb4288c34","type":"paragraph","text":"包括城乡十四个工厂的三百多工人、先进生产者和劳动模向","index":10,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"89145a8690","type":"paragraph","text":"范。","index":11,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"f36fef3501","type":"paragraph","text":"牡丹江水泥厂的工人和他们的家属组了五十六个学习墨克热","index":12,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"9962e54868","type":"paragraph","text":"想列宁主义的小，参加学习的大百七十五人，其中有工人大图二十三人，占金厂总人数的百分之六十三","index":13,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"b4344a3f0d","type":"paragraph","text":"天津市舒多工厂先后了哲学学习班，参加学习的人数已达一万五于余人。","index":14,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"},{"id":"5411362e1a","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉市的拥有一千名学（工人占百分之四十，工发干部起百分之五十）的江汉区业余展列主义学院已开学，汉阳区器列主义业余大学也即将筹备就籍。","index":15,"publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431"}],"page":{"id":"723969de84","publicationId":"0e9d4097-18bc-4064-a098-6fff10cfaa85","articleId":"dbebc62431","start":23,"end":23}}}},"__N_SSG":true}